long_desc.thetext: provide user configurable grouping such as on http://grok.czech.sun.com:8080/source/index.jsp
Vladimir is working on this bug and in first iteration we will get a cli interface to create group definitions, which then can generate front page such as on grok.czech

Created attachment 4323 screenshot of main page with project groups
This page with project groups was generated by crude shell script which traverses the directory with projects and uses simple configuration file which maps projects into group based on regular expression. The final version of the enhancement will be fully implemented within OpenGrok and managed by the OpenGrok script.
Resetting target milestone since this won't make it into 0.10.
